 Did everyone have fun last night?!🎊 Thank you to all our friends who joined us
in celebrating our 3rd Year Anniversary! Thank you ITRI and CIT for your
thoughtful gifts and to our partners XIRI and our member Might electronic for
attending! Special thanks to Alchema, MoonLab, Three Leafs Tea, and Ooh Cha Cha
for stopping by and demoing their products!

 To everyone who has been with us from the beginning, who has supported us
through these 3 years and watched us grow into the company we are now🙌, we
thank you from the bottom of our hearts. Without you all, we would not be where
we are now, and because of your love and support we will continue to grow and
move toward a better future!
🤜🤛
